{"tid":1399462,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"廢老覺醒，由藍轉黃得左！","createTime":"2019-08-03T07:26:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T07:31:58.000Z","uid":77524,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bb3b69b7efc91fa4576fd2d2ebbc0fef87911453","tid":1399462,"uid":77524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T07:26:38.000Z","msg":"話說我訂左啲裝想派街坊<br />\n今朝成大箱運左黎我屋企<br />\n我老母問係咩 問咗幾次我先敢答係<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">豬嘴</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢就屌鳩我話怕我比人拉 點解要支持暴力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後就開始對話 佢真係好擔心我安全<br />\n「我已經唔理你前途係點 但唔好整親你自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n我就同佢講 由6月9號開始我落場見到既事實<br />\n佢又同我分享佢係網上見到既影片<br />\n大家對話左一輪 我媽突然話<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">佢睇果堆全部都係反示威者</span></span>佢結論係 我經歷同佢係網站見到既唔同<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">之後我就幫佢下載左蘋果日報</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢再問我係咪同表姐嘈交 我同佢講翻表姐之前私下話我冇腦既對話 （我表姐係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">深藍</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />成日係親戚群組屌我 宜加日日係群組講打死啲暴徒同黑社會好耶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />） <br />\n<br />\n媽之後叫我退群 我唔肯 再表示自己一個比人屌左咁耐都冇人幫口 佢話陪我<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">一齊退群</span></span>反正留係度冇意思大家都唔會見。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">屌你幾青春！我同老母一齊數321退群啊！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">大家最近啲連儂牆係有用的！<br />\n警察最近做既事係會有報應！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">天滅中共<br />\n8月5罷工<br />\n沒有暴動<br />\n只有暴政<br />\n我愛我媽</span></span>"},{"pid":"619b89cea97d901d8227997a2826c8f204f3cc41","tid":1399462,"uid":171643,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T07:31:58.000Z","msg":"應該同你表姐鬥sd嘛<br />\n佢sd一條你sd十條<br />\n你哋退群 其他係群嘅人就好易俾你表姐洗腦"}]}